dataIdInfo.idAbs: Polygons representing tax parcels in Orange County, Florida. Derived from a variety of source data including; U.S. General Land Office survey plats and notes; Deed descriptions from recorded instruments; Subdivision plats as recorded; Land sales and unrecorded plats; Certified survey maps and plats; State, County, and Municipal Right-of-Way maps; . Each parcel has a parcel identification number (PID) that is used to link information from the CAMA database.
dataIdInfo.idPurp: Polygons in this layer convey the attribute information of the Parcel_Poly layer.
